  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **UNIFYING PRINCIPLE:** Injection occurs whenever **untrusted data** is
  interpreted as **code or commands.** The fix is always: keep data and
  code **structurally separate** --- parameterise, allowlist, encode, and
  never concatenate.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
